Process called "compute_zeta_even_integers" that takes n as Integer, config as ZetaConfig returns Float:
    Note: Compute ζ(2n) using Bernoulli numbers: ζ(2n) = (-1)^{n+1}B_{2n}(2π)^{2n}/(2(2n)!)
    Note: TODO: Implement even integer values with Bernoulli number computation
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Zeta even integers not yet implemented"

Process called "compute_zeta_at_zero" that takes config as ZetaConfig returns Float:
