Process called "compute_zeta_at_negative_integers" that takes n as Integer, config as ZetaConfig returns Float:
    Note: Compute ζ(-n) = -B_{n+1}/(n+1) for positive integer n using Bernoulli numbers
    Note: TODO: Implement negative integer values with Bernoulli relation
    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Zeta negative integers not yet implemented"

Process called "compute_zeta_at_half_integers" that takes n as Integer, config as ZetaConfig returns Float:
